item.title: CVE-2021-21417|2024-08-03T18:09:16.083Z -- fluidsynth -- fluidsynth
item.description: fluidsynth is a software synthesizer based on the SoundFont 2 specifications. A use after free violation was discovered in fluidsynth, that can be triggered when loading an invalid SoundFont file.
